    <div class="section">
        <h2>Director's Statement</h2>
        <blockquote>
            "This film seeks to humanize a legend - showcasing not just 39 PGA Tour wins but Watson's resilience after loss, 
            his advocacy for ALS research, and dedication to nurturing golf's next generation."
        </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>Tom Watson's story transcends golf - a universal narrative about aging, legacy, and resilience. 
        This documentary will position his journey as both a sports chronicle and human drama, appealing to 
        golf enthusiasts and general audiences alike.</p>
        
        <div class="key-scene">
            <h3>Final Frame Concept</h3>
            <p>Watson walking into a Kansas sunset, voiceover of his famous quote: 
            <em>"Golf is a game of life. You don't get what you deserve - you get what you earn."</em></p>
